1970-01-01 00:45:00 Loaf Recipe

  1. Mix all together until well mixed.
  2. Bake at approx 180 deg for about 45mins.

For Variation Add :

  • Currents
  • Mashed Banana (mix together with a few drops of lemon juice to prevent the banana from going black.)
  • Mashed Apple
  • Crushed Pineapple
  •  

Icing

Mix icing sugar (1cup) together with a few drops of water and lemon juice. Enough liquid to make it a runny consistency. Pour over hot loaf and allow to cool before enjoying!!!!
